'''ActivityPub'''是一個基於[[Pump.io|Pump.io]]的ActivityPump協議的一個[[开源软件|開源]]、[[去中心化|去中心化]][[社交網路服務|社交網絡]][[网络传输协议|協議]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zenhack.net/2016/05/29/sandstorm-and-the-social-web.html|title=Sandstorm and the Social Web|website=zenhack.net|date=29 May 2016|access-date=2021-02-10|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030010607/https://zenhack.net/2016/05/29/sandstorm-and-the-social-web.html}}</ref>它爲創作、更新和刪除資料提供一個[[主從式架構|主從式架構]][[應用編程接口|API]]，正如一個爲了傳輸消息和資料的[[联邦宇宙|邦聯的]]伺服器對伺服器[[应用程序接口|API]]。

== 專案狀態 ==
ActivityPub是爲了在[[万维网联盟|万维网联盟]]（W3C）的社交網絡羣體的網絡的一個標準。在早期階段，協議的名稱是“ActivityPump”，但可以感覺到ActivityPub更好地傳遞了該協議的跨越式發布的目的。它學習了名爲[[OStatus|OStatus]]的老一代標準的經驗。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Holloway |first1=James |title=What on Earth is the fediverse and why does it matter? |url=https://newatlas.com/what-is-the-fediverse/56385/ |date=18 September 2018 |website=New Atlas |access-date=3 July 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225021835/https://newatlas.com/what-is-the-fediverse/56385/ }}</ref>

在2018年1月，[[万维网联盟|万维网联盟]]（W3C）當作推薦之一發佈了ActivityPub標準。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.w3.org/TR/2018/REC-activitypub-20180123/|title=W3C Recommendation 23 January 2018|access-date=2021-02-10|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118060630/https://www.w3.org/TR/2018/REC-activitypub-20180123/}}</ref>

W3C社交社區小組每年組織一次免費會議，討論ActivityPub的未來。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://conf.activitypub.rocks|title=ActivityPub Conf 2020|access-date=2022-05-10|archive-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602161023/https://conf.activitypub.rocks/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://redaktor.me/apconf/|title=ActivityPub Conf 2019|access-date=2021-02-10|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308050558/https://redaktor.me/apconf/}}</ref>

前[[Diaspora|Diaspora]]社群經理Sean Tilley撰寫了一篇文章，暗示ActivityPub協議最終可能提供一種聯合網際網路平台的方法。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://medium.com/we-distribute/a-quick-guide-to-the-free-network-c069309f334|title=A quick guide to The Free Network|first=Sean|last=Tilley|date=23 September 2017|access-date=2021-02-10|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124959/https://medium.com/we-distribute/a-quick-guide-to-the-free-network-c069309f334}}</ref>

== 重要範例 ==

=== 邦聯式（伺服器對伺服器）協議 ===
* [[Mastodon|Mastodon]]是一種社交網絡軟體，在2017年9月10日時發布了支援ActivityPub的1.6版。與以前的[[OStatus|OStatus]]協議相比，ActivityPub旨在為私人消息提供更高的安全性。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://activitypub.rocks/implementation-report/|title=Server-Server - ActivityPub implementation reports|access-date=2019-01-02|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406201546/https://activitypub.rocks/implementation-report/}}</ref>
* [[Nextcloud|Nextcloud]]，用於文件託管的邦聯式服務。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Wallen |first1=Jack |title=Nextcloud Social is a promising collaborative feature |url=https://www.techrepublic.com/article/nextcloud-social-is-a-promising-collaborative-feature/ |website=Tech Republic |date=22 January 2019 |access-date=3 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705232335/https://www.techrepublic.com/article/nextcloud-social-is-a-promising-collaborative-feature/ }}</ref>
* [[PeerTube|PeerTube]]，一種用於影片的邦聯式服務。<ref name=":0" />
* {{link-en|Friendica|Friendica}}社交網絡軟件在2019.01版中實現了ActivityPub。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://friendi.ca/2019/01/21/friendica-2019-01-released/|title=Friendica 2019.01 released|access-date=2019-01-24|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301004845/https://friendi.ca/2019/01/21/friendica-2019-01-released/}}</ref>
* Mobilizon，來自{{link-en|Framasoft|Framasoft}}的事件計劃軟體。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nextinpact.com/brief/mobilizon-de-framasoft-gere-maintenant-la-federation-des-installations-10749.htm|title=Mobilizon de Framasoft gère maintenant la fédération des installations - Next INpact|last=actu@nextinpact.com|website=www.nextinpact.com|language=fr|access-date=2019-12-19|archive-date=2020-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200118003907/https://www.nextinpact.com/brief/mobilizon-de-framasoft-gere-maintenant-la-federation-des-installations-10749.htm}}</ref>
* [[Pixelfed|Pixelfed]]，類似於[[Instagram|Instagram]]的邦聯式照片共享平台。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kala Bhavani |first1=Divya |title=Mastodon announces Pixelfed, an open-source alternative to Instagram |url=https://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/technology/internet/mastodon-announces-pixelfed-an-open-source-alternative-to-instagram/article30087768.ece |website=The Hindu |date=27 November 2019 |access-date=3 July 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127210655/https://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/technology/internet/mastodon-announces-pixelfed-an-open-source-alternative-to-instagram/article30087768.ece }}</ref>
* Pleroma是與ActivityPub兼容，資源需求低的微網誌平台。
* [[Misskey|Misskey]]是開源的，是去中心化的微網誌服務。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://wedistribute.org/2019/03/introducing-misskey-a-fediverse-microblogging-app-built-with-node/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-10 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128052510/https://wedistribute.org/2019/03/introducing-misskey-a-fediverse-microblogging-app-built-with-node/ }}</ref>

